---

<footer class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[#0a0a0a] text-white pt-24 pb-12 border-t border-white/10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-12 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 mb-24">
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 pr-8">
        <a href="/" class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
          BUGZERO
        </a>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#a0a0a0] max-w-xs">
          Le service informatique d'Helperiance. Solutions IT professionnelles pour entreprises et particuliers à Monaco, Nice et Menton. Assistance, maintenance, cybersécurité et développement web.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-sm text-[#a0a0a0]">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><iconify-icon icon="solar:phone-linear" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-xl text-[#4f46e5]"></iconify-icon><a href="tel:+33678565430" class="transition-colors hover:text-white">06 78 56 54 30</a></li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><iconify-icon icon="solar:letter-linear" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-xl text-[#4f46e5]"></iconify-icon><a href="mailto:bonjour@bugzero.fr" class="transition-colors hover:text-white">bonjour@bugzero.fr</a></li>
